@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<div class="hero">
    <h1>About Team Kaizen</h1>
    <p>A multidisciplinary team building a centralized help desk and ticket tracking platform for modern software development workflows.</p>
</div>

<div class="content">

    <div class="mission-card">
        <div>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                Team Kaizen is developing a web-based ticket and workflow management system designed to help developers,
                QA analysts, and project managers organize and track requests in one centralized place. Inspired by the
                Japanese philosophy of continuous improvement, our goal is to deliver a functional, user-friendly platform
                using Agile methodology and modern web technologies.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">Meet the Team</div>

    <div class="team-grid">

        <div class="member-card">
            <div class="member-header">
                <div class="avatar av-blue">BC</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="member-name">Branden Cantu</div>
                    <span class="member-role role-dev">Developer</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="member-bio">Branden supports front-end development, HTML page design, UI layout, wireframing, and the visual structure of the platform.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="member-card">
            <div class="member-header">
                <div class="avatar av-amber">BS</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="member-name">Benjamin Sherill</div>
                    <span class="member-role role-pm">Project Manager</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="member-bio">Benjamin leads planning efforts, coordinates deliverables, and provides documentation support throughout the project lifecycle.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="member-card">
            <div class="member-header">
                <div class="avatar av-green">CC</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="member-name">Christina Chamberlain</div>
                    <span class="member-role role-qa">QA Analyst</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="member-bio">Christina leads testing strategy, develops test cases, and ensures the platform meets functional requirements through QA processes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="member-card">
            <div class="member-header">
                <div class="avatar av-amber">DM</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="member-name">Danielle McCartney</div>
                    <span class="member-role role-docs">Documentation</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="member-bio">Danielle supports documentation, research, reports, summaries, and written deliverables for the project.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="member-card">
            <div class="member-header">
                <div class="avatar av-teal">KT</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="member-name">Kyle Tuchon</div>
                    <span class="member-role role-dev">Developer</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="member-bio">Kyle supports C#, UI integration, database architecture, Blazor components, and core back-end functionality.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="tech-section">
        <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
        <div class="tech-grid">
            <div class="tech-chip">ASP.NET Blazor</div>
            <div class="tech-chip">C# / HTML</div>
            <div class="tech-chip">SQL Server</div>
            <div class="tech-chip">GitHub</div>
            <div class="tech-chip">Microsoft Azure</div>
            <div class="tech-chip">Playwright QA</div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>